<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Solicitar Acesso - Sistema de Avaliação de Projetos Escolares</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">

    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-2xl w-full">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-blue-700 mb-6">Solicitação de Acesso para Escolas</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-8">
            Preencha os campos abaixo para solicitar acesso ao nosso sistema. Sua solicitação será analisada pela nossa equipe.
        </p>

        <form action="/solicitar-acesso" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
            <div>
                <label for="nomeEscola" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Nome Completo da Escola <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="nomeEscola" name="nomeEscola" placeholder="Ex: Escola Municipal X" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="cnpj" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">CNPJ da Escola <span class="text-gray-500">(Opcional, mas recomendado)</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="cnpj" name="cnpj" placeholder="XX.XXX.XXX/XXXX-XX" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="endereco" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Endereço Completo da Escola <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="endereco" name="endereco" placeholder="Rua, Número, Bairro, Cidade, Estado, CEP" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="telefoneEscola" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Telefone da Escola <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="tel" id="telefoneEscola" name="telefoneEscola" placeholder="(XX) XXXXX-XXXX" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t pt-6 mt-6 border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Informações do Responsável pelo Contato</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <label for="nomeResponsavel" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Seu Nome Completo (Responsável) <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="nomeResponsavel" name="nomeResponsavel" placeholder="Seu nome" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="emailContato" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Seu E-mail de Contato <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="email" id="emailContato" name="emailContato" placeholder="seu.email@escola.com.br" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="cargoResponsavel" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Seu Cargo na Escola <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="cargoResponsavel" name="cargoResponsavel" placeholder="Ex: Diretor(a), Coordenador(a), Professor(a)" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="telefoneContato" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Seu Telefone de Contato <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="tel" id="telefoneContato" name="telefoneContato" placeholder="(XX) XXXXX-XXXX" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t pt-6 mt-6 border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Sobre o Uso do Sistema</h3>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="tipoEvento" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Qual tipo de evento você planeja organizar? <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <select id="tipoEvento" name="tipoEvento" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" required>
                    <option value="">Selecione...</option>
                    <option value="feira_ciencias">Feira de Ciências</option>
                    <option value="mostra_cultural">Mostra Cultural</option>
                    <option value="jornada_academica">Jornada Acadêmica</option>
                    <option value="evento_multidisciplinar">Evento Multidisciplinar</option>
                    <option value="outro">Outro (especifique na mensagem)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="previsaoUso" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Quando você pretende começar a usar o sistema? <span class="text-gray-500">(Opcional)</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="previsaoUso" name="previsaoUso" placeholder="Ex: Próximo semestre, Agosto de 2025" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label for="mensagem" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Mensagem Adicional / Objetivo da Solicitação</label>
                <textarea id="mensagem" name="mensagem" rows="5" placeholder="Descreva brevemente como sua escola pretende utilizar o sistema e o que esperam alcançar." class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 resize-y"></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out">
                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane mr-2"></i> Enviar Solicitação de Acesso
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>